<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Gender Reveal Games | FIORE</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/Gender Reveal gamesCss.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-section-genderrevealgames">
    <div class="hero-content-genderrevealgames">
      <h1 class="fade-in-up-genderrevealgames">Let the Games Begin!</h1>
      <p class="fade-in-up-genderrevealgames delay">Create unforgettable moments with playful and interactive games.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Game Ideas Grid -->
  <section class="section-genderrevealgames">
    <h2>Popular Gender Reveal Games</h2>
    <div class="grid-genderrevealgames">
      <div class="card-genderrevealgames">
        <img src="/img/votingGenderReveal.jpeg" alt="Guess the Gender">
        <h3>Guess the Gender</h3>
        <p>Have guests vote Team Pink or Team Blue using pins, cards, or jars.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-genderrevealgames">
        <img src="/img/Old Wives Tales.jpeg" alt="Old Wives’ Tales Quiz">
        <h3>Old Wives’ Tales Quiz</h3>
        <p>Use fun myths and superstitions to guess the baby’s gender together!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-genderrevealgames">
        <img src="/img/Bingo Game.jpeg" alt="Gender Reveal Bingo">
        <h3>Gender Reveal Bingo</h3>
        <p>Create a custom bingo sheet with predictions about names, features, etc.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-genderrevealgames">
        <img src="/img/Gender Reveal Voting.jpeg" alt="Team Station">
        <h3>Team Voting Station</h3>
        <p>Let guests wear pink or blue badges to show their guess!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-genderrevealgames">
        <img src="/img/photo booth.jpeg" alt="Photo Booth">
        <h3>Photo Booth Fun</h3>
        <p>Use props, signs, and fun backgrounds for guests to capture memories.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-genderrevealgames">
        <img src="/img/Baby Tune.jpeg" alt="Name That Tune">
        <h3>Name That Baby Tune</h3>
        <p>Play baby-related songs and have guests guess them for prizes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-genderrevealgames">
        <img src="/img/Guess the baby stats baby.jpeg" alt="Baby Stats">
        <h3>Guess the Baby Stats</h3>
        <p>Guests predict baby's arrival details on cute cards or a chalkboard.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-genderrevealgames">
        <img src="/img/Gender Reveal Balloon Pop Game.jpeg" alt="Baby Stats">
        <h3></h3>
        <p>Guests pop balloons filled with pink or blue confetti to reveal their gender guesses in a burst of fun!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Keepsake Section -->
  <section class="section-genderrevealgames">
    <h2>Make It Memorable</h2>
    <ul class="tips-box-genderrevealgames">
      <li>Set up a guestbook with space for wishes and baby name ideas.</li>
      <li>Give winners scented candles, sweet jars, or baby-themed trinkets.</li>
      <li>Create a gender reveal memory wall with photos and notes from guests.</li>
      <li>Design a scratch-off gender reveal game — guests scratch to reveal pink or blue!</li>
      <li>Host a mini "Old Wives’ Tales" trivia and tally team guesses.</li>
      <li>Provide a box of "future advice" where guests drop wisdom notes for the baby or parents.</li>
      <li>Set up a balloon pop game — one with colored confetti inside for the big reveal!</li>
      <li>Include a “Guess the Birth Date” board where everyone pins their predictions.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
